# ===================================================================
# Ledgerline .gitignore — Xcode 16 / Swift 6 / SwiftData / CloudKit
# ===================================================================

# ---- macOS noise ----
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon?
._*

# ---- Xcode user state (NEVER commit — per-developer, churns constantly) ----
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

# ---- Build products & derived data ----
build/
DerivedData/
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

# ---- Swift Package Manager ----
# Keep Package.resolved COMMITTED (reproducible dependency pins).
# Ignore only local build/workspace artifacts:
.swiftpm/
.build/

# ---- Playgrounds (scratch work while exploring CloudKit APIs) ----
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace
*.playground/playground.xcworkspace

# ---- Test artifacts ----
*.xcresult

# ---- Local database files (Phase 2 "Inspect the SQLite" depth move) ----
# Any store files copied out of the simulator/device container for
# inspection stay local — INTERNALS.md documents findings; the raw
# stores are throwaway evidence, not source.
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-wal
*.store
LocalStores/

# ---- Secrets & local-only config ----
# CloudKit needs no API keys (auth rides the iCloud account — that's
# the point), but keep the habit: anything matching these never lands
# in a public portfolio repo.
*.p8
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
*.cer
.env
.env.*
secrets.*

# ---- CI / tooling (future-proofing, harmless now) ----
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output

# ===================================================================
# Deliberately COMMITTED (do not add these):
#   - Ledgerline.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj   (the project itself)
#   - Package.resolved                        (reproducible builds)
#   - *.xcscheme in xcshareddata/             (shared schemes → CI)
#   - docs/, SCHEMA.md, INTERNALS.md, ARCHITECTURE.md (the artifact!)
# ===================================================================